// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1032 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c59db16b-2a5b-5cc5-a8db-23d175bf280d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*")
